										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Traffic is great, but itâ€™s optimizing your conversion rate thatâ€™ll grow your business. This list of conversion rate optimization statistics will help you benchmark your current results and give you data-backed strategies to get more conversions from every campaign.</p>
