<h3>Salesforce cut through the noise to reach millennial business decision-makers</h3>
<p>In an effort to reach millennial B2B buyers during their downtime, <a href="https://ads.spotify.com/en-US/inspiration/salesforce-advertising-campaign/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Salesforce</a> ran multi-format campaigns&#8211;a combination of audio, <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2019/05/23/google-display-ads">display</a>, and video takeover&#8211;across playlists and podcasts that were relevant.</p>
<p>The result? Salesforce boosted brand affinity (+10%), consideration (+11%), and unaided recall (+30%) among business decision-makers.</p>
<h3>Neutrogena connected with health and beauty buyers to promote anti-acne products</h3>
<p>To promote their latest acne-fighting product line, <a href="https://ads.spotify.com/en-US/inspiration/neutrogena-case-study/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Neutrogena</a> used Spotifyâ€™s first and third-party data to engage with health and beauty product consumers through digital audio and display ads.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/spotify-advertising-example-neutrogena.jpg" alt="spotify advertising example from neutrogena" width="774" height="599" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-73611" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/spotify-advertising-example-neutrogena.jpg 774w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/spotify-advertising-example-neutrogena-480x371.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 774px, 100vw" /></p>
